```
Phase 2 ML Predictions
  └── LSTMInference (volume forecast + MC Dropout CI)
  └── XGBoostClassifier (breach probability)
  └── TFT Forecaster (quantile q10/q50/q90)
          │
          ▼
phase3_simulation/
  ├── simpy_engine.py        ← Core discrete-event queue simulator
  ├── monte_carlo.py         ← 1,000-run parallelised orchestrator
  ├── scenario_builder.py    ← What-if scenario configurator
