## Integration with Phase 2

Phase 2 outputs feed Phase 3 in two ways:

| Phase 2 Output | Phase 3 Usage |
|---|---|
| `LSTMInference.predict()` → `mean['1h']` | Sets `arrival_rate` in `QueueConfig` (ML-driven simulation) |
| `XGBoostClassifier` breach probability | Overlaid on simulation breach rate for cross-validation |
| `TFTForecaster` q10/q90 quantiles | Used as P10/P90 bounds for arrival rate uncertainty |
| `DriftMonitor` PSI score | If PSI > 0.2, simulation uses widened arrival rate variance |

