## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `python -m phase3_simulation.runner --scenario baseline --runs 100 --horizon 4` — Smoke test
- Verify `SimulationResult` fields are non-null and in valid ranges
- Verify Mann-Whitney U p-values are meaningful (agent_reduction should be < 0.05 vs baseline)
- Verify HTML report is generated and non-empty
- Verify JSON export is valid and parseable

### Statistical Sanity Checks
- Baseline breach rate should be in range [5%, 25%] for Payment Processing (matches empirical)
- `agent_reduction_2` P50 breach rate must be > `baseline` P50 (monotonicity)
- `agent_add_2_payment` P50 breach rate must be < `baseline` P50

### Manual Verification
- Open HTML report in browser and confirm all 5 charts render correctly
- Confirm narrative text is generated for worst-case scenarios

